main event: Sighting of 3 round, white objects in the background sky over Atlantic City, New Jersey.
interesting points: The objects were observed for about 30 seconds before disappearing., Probable explanation for the sighting was aircraft., Negative report received from Naval and Air Force Bases regarding jets in the area., The objects were moving north., The sighting was part of a report submitted to Project Blue Book.
sighted object: three round, white objects in the sky
